      "lede-rich-text":
        '<p>US residents can now buy STX directly through the Hiro Wallet browser extension with a credit card, debit card, or bank transfer via integrations with <a href="https://www.moonpay.com/">MoonPay</a> and <a href="https://transak.com/">Transak</a>. Take advantage of 0% fees on STX purchases via MoonPay until April 9th and via Transak until April 12th.</p>',
      name: "US Residents Can Now Buy STX \tThrough the Hiro Wallet",
      "post-body":
        '<p>For the first time, US residents can now purchase STX directly through the Hiro Wallet browser extension. Through the Hiro Wallet, users can access dozens of applications built on Stacks, including mining CityCoins, minting NFTs, lending assets on a DeFi protocol, and more.</p><p>Stacks is the largest and fastest-growing Web3 project on Bitcoin, and we are proud to support the Stacks ecosystem by providing best-in-class products and services. As a developer tools company, our goal with this latest integration is to improve user onboarding so developers can deliver the best experience for their users.</p><p>To celebrate this announcement, MoonPay is offering a promotion of 0% fees on STX purchases until April 9th. Transak is offering 0% fees on STX purchases until April 12th.</p><blockquote>Take advantage of 0% fees on STX purchases via MoonPay until April 9th and via Transak until April 12th.</blockquote><h2>How It Works</h2><p>Under the ‚Äúbuy‚Äù option in the Hiro Wallet browser extension, users will see the option to buy on MoonPay and Transak.</p><p>MoonPay accepts all major payment methods, including Visa, Mastercard, Apple Pay, Google Pay, Samsung Pay, SEPA, Faster Payments, Wire Transfers, Open Banking and ACH. Transak supports payments via credit card and debit card with more methods coming soon. Fees, daily limits and payment methods vary by country.&nbsp;</p><p>If you are using either of these integration partners for the first time, you may need to verify your account through a process known as ‚ÄúKYC,‚Äù or ‚Äúknow your customer.‚Äù Please refer to <a href="https://support.moonpay.com/hc/en-gb">MoonPay Support</a> and <a href="https://support.transak.com/hc/en-us">Transak Support</a> if you have any questions.</p><p>Please note: this feature is not currently available for the Hiro Wallet desktop application.&nbsp;</p><h2>Download the Hiro Wallet</h2><p>The Hiro Wallet is the #1 wallet in the Stacks ecosystem and is available in both the Chrome and Firefox stores. Download your wallet today to begin exploring on Stacks!</p><p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/stacks-wallet/ldinpeekobnhjjdofggfgjlcehhmanlj">Install for Chrome</a> | <a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/hiro-wallet/">Install for Firefox</a></p><p>Need more help? <a href="http://stacks.chat/">Join us on Discord</a> and head to the #üí∞‰∏®wallet channel with your questions.</p>',
