      "lede-rich-text":
        '<p>Calling all Stacks developers. We want to make it easier for you to build Bitcoin applications by providing best-in-class developer tools. Help us improve our products by telling us about your experience in a <a href="https://survey.hiro.so/">short 10 minute survey</a>.</p>',
      name: "Help Us Improve Hiro Products",
      "post-body":
        '<p>The growth we‚Äôve seen in the Stacks ecosystem has <a href="https://from0to.hiro.so/">outpaced our wildest expectations</a>. We are the largest and fastest-growing Web3 project on Bitcoin, and most Hiro tools are less than one year old (!).&nbsp;<br></p><p>We have lots of new features and improvements planned, and we want to hear from you about your experience. Your feedback will help us prioritize and make key product decisions in the 2022 Hiro roadmap.<br></p><p>As a thank you for taking the survey, we‚Äôll send you some special Hiro swag. To receive it, just fill out your shipping information at the optional last question. And if you want to remain anon, Anon, you can leave that blank and know that we are grateful for your feedback!</p><figure class="w-richtext-figure-type-image w-richtext-align-center" style="max-width:408.5px" data-rt-type="image" data-rt-align="center" data-rt-max-width="408.5px"><a href="https://survey.hiro.so/" target="_blank"><div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/5ff21113877dd79ed7913b57/62152e51345045cc48bafc84_Asset%2014.png" loading="lazy" width="auto" height="auto"></div></a></figure><p>‚Äç<br></p>',
