        '<p>Non-US residents can now purchase STX directly within the Hiro web wallet with a credit card, debit cart or bank deposit via an integration with <a href="https://transak.com/">Transak</a>.<br></p>',
      name: "Funding Your Hiro Wallet Just Got Easier",
      "post-body":
        '<p>Funding your Hiro wallet just got easier. Users will now see a ‚ÄúBuy‚Äù option in the Hiro Wallet web extension. STX purchases are facilitated via an integration with Transak.* Once the purchase is completed, STX will arrive directly into your wallet.</p><figure class="w-richtext-figure-type-image w-richtext-align-center" style="max-width:1004px" data-rt-type="image" data-rt-align="center" data-rt-max-width="1004px"><div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/5ff21113877dd79ed7913b57/61ae43fd725e1f9f71aedfb3_Frame%205465.png" loading="lazy"></div></figure><p>The Hiro wallet lets you connect with over 50 applications in the Stacks ecosystem. You can mint NFTs, take out a loan, mine CityCoins, and so much more.<br></p><h3>Take advantage of 0% fees on STX purchases until December 19th, 23:59 CET.<br></h3><p>Transak is supported in over 60 countries; a detailed list of currency coverage and fees can be found <a href="https://www.notion.so/Currency-Coverage-and-Fees-for-Buying-Crypto-976ee96fc0764628ba990b550b1310d3">here</a>. Fees and payment methods vary by country. Transak also shows you average slippage and processing times when making a purchase.</p><figure class="w-richtext-figure-type-image w-richtext-align-center" style="max-width:496px" data-rt-type="image" data-rt-align="center" data-rt-max-width="496px"><div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/5ff21113877dd79ed7913b57/61ae2f9d1aafc9e5e39f4d42_Screenshot%202021-12-06%20at%2012.42.48.png" loading="lazy"></div></figure><p>‚Äç<br></p><p>If you are using Transak for the first time, you may need to verify your account through a process known as ‚ÄúKYC‚Äù. Please refer to the <a href="https://support.transak.com/hc/en-us">Transak support page</a> if you have any questions.<br></p><p>Please note: Transak does <strong>not</strong> currently support STX purchases in the US. In the months ahead, we plan to add more options for fiat on-ramps for US-based users and ACH/ bank transfers.</p><figure class="w-richtext-figure-type-image w-richtext-align-fullwidth" style="max-width:1079px" data-rt-type="image" data-rt-align="fullwidth" data-rt-max-width="1079px"><div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/5ff21113877dd79ed7913b57/61001f37d9b8a89b4411a7bd_Asset%2028.png" loading="lazy" width="auto" height="auto"></div></figure><p><br></p><h2>Download the Hiro Wallet</h2><p>As the Stacks ecosystem continues to grow, Hiro is dedicated to empowering developers with world-class apps and tools. The wallet extension provided by Hiro PBC for interacting with the Stacks blockchain is available in both the Chrome and Firefox stores.<br></p><ul><li><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/stacks-wallet/ldinpeekobnhjjdofggfgjlcehhmanlj">Install for Chrome or Brave</a></li><li>‚Äç<a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/hiro-wallet/">Install for Firefox</a></li></ul><p><a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/hiro-wallet/">‚Äç</a><br>Need more help? <a href="http://stacks.chat/">Join us on Discord</a> and head to the <a href="https://discord.gg/PKVetN9vEW">#üí∞‰∏®wallet </a>channel with your questions.</p>',
